  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 570f073b49457d647ad7eacd7abba8f9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialogue_1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - Hello my young student!... Actually, I'm calling you because I was urgently called
    to a research conference in the city, so I'll be gone for a week and all my orders
    are on you...
  - 'But look at it this way: how can you learn more effectively than through practice?
    You don''t have a choice anyway.'
  - So, the most important things you'll need to be in the main hall for your medicines
    are the cauldron and the synthesis table. You'll use them most often.
  - At the synthesis table, you'll create other compounds by combining basic elements.
    These are needed in most potions.
  - The cauldron is what you use when brewing every potion. It has two important
    systems - temperature and state of matter - which need to be adjusted for each
    potion!
  - I think I've said all the most important things, the first pet should arrive
    soon, lucky student!
  characterIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ad864c0ad8fea674b922ba8cc177ee40, type: 3}
  autoAdvanceDelay: 2
